title: Highlights | Arsenal Women 1 - 0 Leicester City
body_text:
Frida Maanum netted the only goal of the game to see us get past Leicester City in the WSL, and you can see the best of the action in our highlights package.
We bounced back from the disappointment of losing in the semi-finals of the Champions League by moving to within six points of leaders Manchester United thanks to our Norwegian midfielder's superb strike midway through the second half.
Take a look at the best of the action by pressing play on the video above.
